snippet.title: Trailer Crumble - free 3D platformer destruction demo
snippet.description:
Crumble is a dynamic physic platformer. Try not to fall in an increasingly crumbling world.
Wishlist and play the demo on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1061180/Crumble/
Visit us: https://www.bruteforce-games.com/

"Music: www.bensound.com"
